description: The ripped Markus Kage has long been viciously training for an upcoming boxing match, only to be notified of it’s sudden cancellation. Disappointed and frustrated, he needs to find a way to make some fast cash. After receiving a tip from his trainer, he researches a potentially lucrative avenue online called ‘Friendly Fire’. This unorthodox option involving two other men, Ryan Stone, and Jay Dymel, may be the solution to far more than just his financial problems.
title: Friendly Fire, Part 1:Jay Dymel. Markus Kage, Ryan Stone RAW
